metadata.dc:description: At the service of Human Reproduction of the Centro Médico Nacional "20 de Noviembre" ISSSTE from January 94 to August 98, at the first visit, were performed routine screening for antibodies anti-HIV for both partners. Of 672 samples 3 (0.44%) were positive for antibodies anti-HIV with ELISA and two confirmed by Western blot analysis.
metadata.dc:title: Prevalencia de anticuerpos anti-VIH en pacientes del servicio de Biología de la Reproducción Humana del Centro Médico Nacional "20 de Noviembre" del I.S.S.S.T.E.
[Prevalence of anti-HIV antibodies in patients at the Service of Human Reproduction Biology of the "20th November" National Medical Center].
